reviewText: Not what I expected. Guess I should have read the description better.
Don't know why this was even a 3D. not very good

The 3D on this is odd, I really don't believe that it was natively photographed  but by some type of software conversion.  There are a few odd effects, as in the narrator's shirt comes forward and his arms much further back.  Would recomend Ghost Hunters over this first but it is a good first effort.
